Houston Employees:

Paychecks for the 3/28 pay date will be available to be picked up (ECS 05852, Fifth Floor) this Wednesday March 27th at the following times.  In order to keep the lines short, please try to arrive during the following times.  We will need to have you show us a picture ID (Security Badge) and sign off that you received your check.

Last Names Beginning with:

 A - G:  1:00 - 1:30 pm
 H - M:  1:30 - 2:00 pm
 N - S:   2:00 - 2:30 pm
 T - Z:    2:30 - 3:00 pm
                                         
Items to be aware of this time around include the following:

Direct Deposit started for many of you this pay period, however I do have your earnings statements to be picked up.
Employees with bus passes will notice that the bus pass amount will appear as both an earnings code and a deduction code, in order for imputed income to be calculated (GTL).

Portland Employees:

Paychecks for Portland employees will be distributed by Mollie Gustafson, later this afternoon.


